{"tid":1577802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"槍擊要犯　救雞和尚也參選台灣總統","createTime":"2019-09-18T01:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T01:21:39.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0fb6c16cf26c7d2be41ac7643b15cbbc8bc9eb","tid":1577802,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"2019-09-18<br />\n兩岸要聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190918/large/1568737519_1b9f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568737519_1b9f.gif&h=80463b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n登記成為台灣正副總統選舉的被聯署人的程序昨下午5時30分正式截止。據中選會統計，這次共有8組正副總統被連署人完成申請登記作業，除了前副總統呂秀蓮、新黨籍參選人楊世光等「正經人家」候選人，亦有「救雞和尚」及「台灣十大槍擊要犯」等人參與，充滿特色。<br />\n<br />\n呂秀蓮獲公民提名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中選會本月13日開放登記，自稱「第一個出家人登記選總統」的禪師釋悟善成為首位登記人，更即日付清100萬元新台幣（下同，約25.7萬港元）保證金。據悉，現年59歲的釋悟善最出名的事迹是不顧危險闖高速公路救雞，競選理念為兩岸和平、經濟穩定，希望終止藍綠惡鬥。釋悟善發言人表示，釋悟善信眾多，有信心跨過聯署門檻。<br />\n<br />\n除代表善的佛門中人，惡名昭彰的台灣十大槍擊要犯藍信祺也打算競選總統。1981年年僅16歲的藍犯下「虎山雙屍命案」，21歲「躍升」為台灣十大槍擊要犯。現年54歲的他繼2011、2015年後再度以「世界台灣皇帝」身份宣佈參選總統，早前參選時曾表示「不支持我者都會死」，為此更被警方約談。</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣總統選舉有「政黨推薦」及「公民聯署」兩種提名推薦程序，民進黨及國民黨則會走政黨推薦程序。在公民聯署方面，今次共有8組申證成為被聯署人，包括前副總統呂秀蓮。根據規定，被連署人須繳交100萬元連署保證金，並在9月19日至11月2日取得283,840萬份連署證明書，才可於11月18日至20日登記成為正副總統候選人。<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/daily/article/20190918/20770243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20770243&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5P3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b53913dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20770243&h=500c7492\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/daily/article/20190918/20770243</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da001469201e6257b357c0a38a68eac6ed55ca3e","tid":1577802,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"552afdece238922ff4ec871d66d55d1e1275e178","tid":1577802,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"ffcce0e1bf5aed04eca588be5d22effcafec3b9e","tid":1577802,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:21:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi